  Add github to remote-id in metadata.xml

  03 May 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> ferret-0.11.8.6.ebuild:
  Avoid test know to fail and possible crash ruby, fixing bug 438412.

*ferret-0.11.8.6 (21 Feb 2015)

  21 Feb 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +ferret-0.11.8.6.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add ruby22.

  21 May 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> ferret-0.11.8.5-r2.ebuild:
  Remove ruby18 target.

*ferret-0.11.8.5-r2 (29 Jan 2014)

  29 Jan 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +ferret-0.11.8.5-r2.ebuild,
