  Add ruby20, ruby21 support. Cleanup old.

  11 Aug 2013; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -ferret-0.11.8.4.ebuild,
  -ferret-0.11.8.5.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

